Package: clrng
Type: Package
Title: Parallel Random Number Generation on GPU in R
Description: Builds on gpuR and utilizes the clRNG ('OpenCL') library to provide efficient tools to generate independent random numbers in parallel on a GPU and save the results as R objects, and ensuring high-quality random numbers even when R is used interactively or in an ad-hoc manner.
